{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":700,"text":"My name is Emiliano Salinas"},{"time":2200,"text":"and I'm going to talk about the role"},{"time":6400,"text":"we members of society play"},{"time":8500,"text":"in the violent atmosphere"},{"time":9800,"text":"this country is living in right now."},{"time":13140,"text":"I was born in 1976."},{"time":16200,"text":"I grew up in a traditional Mexican family."},{"time":19600,"text":"As a child, I had a pretty normal life:"},{"time":21600,"text":"I would go to school, play with my friends and cousins."},{"time":25700,"text":"But then my father became President of Mexico"},{"time":28000,"text":"and my life changed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31500,"text":"What I'm about to say,"},{"time":33800,"text":"at least some of what I'm about to say,"},{"time":35300,"text":"will cause controversy."},{"time":37100,"text":"Firstly, because I'm the one who's going to say it."},{"time":40200,"text":"And secondly, because what I'm going to say is true,"},{"time":43200,"text":"and it will make a lot of people nervous"},{"time":45200,"text":"because it's something we don't want to hear."},{"time":47850,"text":"But it's imperative that we listen"},{"time":49900,"text":"because it's undeniable and definitive."},{"time":52258,"text":"It will also make members of"},{"time":54000,"text":"criminal organizations nervous"},{"time":55935,"text":"for the same reasons."},{"time":57700,"text":"I'm going to talk about the role"},{"time":60900,"text":"we members of society play"},{"time":62738,"text":"in this phenomenon,"},{"time":64300,"text":"and about four different response levels"},{"time":66000,"text":"we citizens have against violence."},{"time":70300,"text":"I know many will find it difficult to separate the fact"},{"time":72500,"text":"that I'm Carlos Salinas de Gortari's son"},{"time":74400,"text":"from the fact that I'm a citizen"},{"time":76200,"text":"concerned about the country's current situation."},{"time":78000,"text":"Don't worry."},{"time":79200,"text":"It's not necessary for understanding"},{"time":81200,"text":"the importance of what I'm going to say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84700,"text":"I think we have a problem in Mexico."},{"time":86400,"text":"We have a big problem."},{"time":87700,"text":"I think there's consensus on this."},{"time":89700,"text":"No one argues --"},{"time":90700,"text":"we all agree there's a problem."},{"time":92000,"text":"What we don't agree on"},{"time":93500,"text":"is what the problem actually is."},{"time":96800,"text":"Is it the Zetas? The drug traffickers? The government?"},{"time":101500,"text":"Corruption? Poverty? Or is it something else?"},{"time":105700,"text":"I think none of these is the problem."},{"time":107900,"text":"I don't mean they don't deserve attention."},{"time":110200,"text":"But we won't be able to take care of any of those things"},{"time":112670,"text":"if we don't solve the real problem"},{"time":114800,"text":"we have in Mexico first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116300,"text":"The real problem we have is"},{"time":117690,"text":"most of us Mexicans, we believe we are victims"},{"time":120900,"text":"of our circumstances."},{"time":122646,"text":"We are a country of victims."},{"time":125000,"text":"Historically, we've always acted as victims"},{"time":127750,"text":"of something or somebody."},{"time":129520,"text":"We were victims of the Spaniards."},{"time":131800,"text":"Then we were victims of the French."},{"time":133820,"text":"Then we were victims of Don Porfirio."},{"time":136264,"text":"Then we were victims of the PRI."},{"time":138416,"text":"Even of Salinas."},{"time":140100,"text":"And of El Peje."},{"time":142221,"text":"And now of the Zetas and the traffickers and the criminals and the kidnappers ..."},{"time":145207,"text":"Hold on! Wait a minute!"},{"time":147687,"text":"What if none of these things is the problem?"},{"time":151222,"text":"The problem is not the things we feel victims of."},{"time":154525,"text":"The problem is that we play the role of victims."},{"time":158725,"text":"We need to open our eyes and see that we are not victims."},{"time":162500,"text":"If only we stopped feeling like victims,"},{"time":164700,"text":"if we stopped acting as victims,"},{"time":166000,"text":"our country would change so much!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":169235,"text":"I'm going to talk about how to go from a society"},{"time":172700,"text":"that acts as a victim of circumstances"},{"time":174399,"text":"to a responsible, involved society"},{"time":177300,"text":"that takes the future of its country in its own hands."},{"time":180836,"text":"I'm going to talk about four different levels"},{"time":183300,"text":"of civil response against violence,"},{"time":185400,"text":"from weakest"},{"time":187700,"text":"to strongest."},{"time":190000,"text":"The first level, the weakest level of civil response against violence,"},{"time":192500,"text":"is denial and apathy."},{"time":195400,"text":"Today, much of Mexican society is in denial"},{"time":198000,"text":"of the situation we're going through."},{"time":201000,"text":"We want to go on with our daily life"},{"time":203258,"text":"even though we are not living under normal circumstances."},{"time":205800,"text":"Daily life in our country is,"},{"time":208500,"text":"to say the least,"},{"time":211729,"text":"under extraordinary, exceptional circumstances."},{"time":213693,"text":"It's like someone who has a serious illness"},{"time":217500,"text":"and pretends it's the flu"},{"time":219500,"text":"and it will just go away."},{"time":221470,"text":"We want to pretend that Mexico has the flu."},{"time":224711,"text":"But it doesn't."},{"time":226813,"text":"Mexico has cancer."},{"time":229030,"text":"And if we don't do something about it,"},{"time":231200,"text":"the cancer will end up killing it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234354,"text":"We need to move Mexican society"},{"time":236800,"text":"from denial and apathy"},{"time":238800,"text":"to the next level of citizen response,"},{"time":241200,"text":"which is, effectively, recognition."},{"time":244332,"text":"And that recognition will sow fear --"},{"time":248166,"text":"recognizing the seriousness of the situation."},{"time":251325,"text":"But, fear is better than apathy"},{"time":254972,"text":"because fear makes us do something."},{"time":258286,"text":"Many people in Mexico"},{"time":261529,"text":"are afraid today."},{"time":263486,"text":"We're very afraid."},{"time":264962,"text":"And we're acting out of that fear."},{"time":267100,"text":"And let me tell you what the problem is"},{"time":268800,"text":"with acting out of fear --"},{"time":270500,"text":"and this is the second level of civil response:"},{"time":273000,"text":"fear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274600,"text":"Let's think about Mexican streets:"},{"time":277000,"text":"they're unsafe because of violence,"},{"time":280500,"text":"so people stay at home."},{"time":283000,"text":"Does that make streets more or less safe?"},{"time":287200,"text":"Less safe!"},{"time":288200,"text":"So streets become more desolate and unsafe,"},{"time":290000,"text":"so we stay home more --"},{"time":291400,"text":"which makes streets even more desolate and unsafe,"},{"time":293800,"text":"and we stay home even more."},{"time":295300,"text":"This vicious circle ends up with the whole population"},{"time":298000,"text":"stuck inside their houses, scared to death --"},{"time":300000,"text":"even more afraid than when we were out on the streets."},{"time":302500,"text":"We need to confront this fear."},{"time":305000,"text":"We need to move Mexican society,"},{"time":307400,"text":"the members of society who are at this level,"},{"time":310000,"text":"to the next level, which is action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312200,"text":"We need to face our fears and take back our streets,"},{"time":316200,"text":"our cities, our neighborhoods."},{"time":319000,"text":"For many people, acting involves courage."},{"time":325200,"text":"We go from fear to courage."},{"time":327200,"text":"They say, \"I can't take it anymore."},{"time":330000,"text":"Let's do something about it.\""},{"time":333000,"text":"Recently --"},{"time":335000,"text":"this is a sensitive figure --"},{"time":338000,"text":"35 public lynchings have been recorded"},{"time":341200,"text":"so far in 2010"},{"time":342800,"text":"in Mexico."},{"time":347000,"text":"Usually it's one or two a year."},{"time":350400,"text":"Now we're experiencing one every week."},{"time":353000,"text":"This shows that society is desperate"},{"time":356000,"text":"and it's taking the law into its own hands."},{"time":359500,"text":"Unfortunately, violent action --"},{"time":362000,"text":"though action is better than no action --"},{"time":365000,"text":"but taking part in it"},{"time":368000,"text":"only disguises violence."},{"time":370500,"text":"If I'm violent with you"},{"time":373000,"text":"and you respond with violence,"},{"time":375000,"text":"you become part of the violence"},{"time":377000,"text":"and you just disguise my violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381000,"text":"So civil action"},{"time":383200,"text":"is vital,"},{"time":385000,"text":"but it's also vital to take people"},{"time":387000,"text":"who are at the level of courage"},{"time":389200,"text":"and violent action"},{"time":391000,"text":"to the next level,"},{"time":393000,"text":"which is non-violent action."},{"time":394600,"text":"It's pacific, coordinated civil action,"},{"time":397500,"text":"which doesn't mean passive action."},{"time":399500,"text":"It means it's determined and effective,"},{"time":402300,"text":"but not violent."},{"time":404800,"text":"There are examples of this kind of action in Mexico."},{"time":407500,"text":"Two years ago, in Galena City, Chihuahua,"},{"time":412200,"text":"a member of the community was kidnapped,"},{"time":414000,"text":"Eric Le Barón."},{"time":415700,"text":"His brothers, Benjamín and Julián,"},{"time":417300,"text":"got together with the rest of the community"},{"time":419300,"text":"to think of the best course of action:"},{"time":421700,"text":"to pay the ransom,"},{"time":423800,"text":"to take up arms and go after the kidnappers"},{"time":428300,"text":"or to ask the government for help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430600,"text":"In the end, Benjamín and Julián decided"},{"time":433000,"text":"the best thing they could do"},{"time":435000,"text":"was to organize the community and act together."},{"time":437800,"text":"So what did they do?"},{"time":439500,"text":"They mobilized the whole community of Le Barón"},{"time":441800,"text":"to go to Chihuahua,"},{"time":444600,"text":"where they organized a sit-in"},{"time":447000,"text":"in the central park of the city."},{"time":449300,"text":"They sent a message to the kidnappers:"},{"time":451200,"text":"\"If you want your ransom come and get it."},{"time":454200,"text":"We'll be waiting for you right here.\""},{"time":456600,"text":"They stayed there."},{"time":458600,"text":"Seven days later, Eric was set free"},{"time":461100,"text":"and was able to return home."},{"time":463100,"text":"This is an example of what an organized society can do,"},{"time":466900,"text":"a society that acts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469500,"text":"Of course, criminals can respond."},{"time":471700,"text":"And in this case, they did."},{"time":473700,"text":"On July 7th, 2009,"},{"time":477000,"text":"Benjamín Le Barón was murdered."},{"time":479500,"text":"But Julián Le Barón keeps working"},{"time":482200,"text":"and he has been mobilizing communities in Chihuahua"},{"time":484400,"text":"for over a year."},{"time":487000,"text":"And for over a year he has known that a price has been put on his head."},{"time":489700,"text":"But he keeps fighting."},{"time":491500,"text":"He keeps organizing."},{"time":493000,"text":"He keeps mobilizing."},{"time":495000,"text":"These heroic acts are present all over the country."},{"time":497600,"text":"With a thousand Juliáns working together,"},{"time":500000,"text":"Mexico would be a very different country."},{"time":502000,"text":"And they're out there!"},{"time":503500,"text":"They just have to raise their hands."},{"time":508000,"text":"I was born in Mexico, I grew up in Mexico"},{"time":514000,"text":"and along the way, I learned to love Mexico."},{"time":519000,"text":"I think anyone who has stepped foot on this land --"},{"time":522200,"text":"not to mention all Mexican people --"},{"time":524200,"text":"will agree that it's not difficult"},{"time":527000,"text":"to love Mexico."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530000,"text":"I've traveled a lot"},{"time":532500,"text":"and nowhere else have I found the passion Mexicans have."},{"time":538000,"text":"That devotion we feel"},{"time":540000,"text":"for the national football team."},{"time":542000,"text":"That devotion we show"},{"time":544000,"text":"in helping victims of disasters,"},{"time":546000,"text":"such as the earthquake in 1985"},{"time":548000,"text":"or this year's floods."},{"time":550500,"text":"The passion with which we've been singing the national anthem"},{"time":556000,"text":"since we were kids."},{"time":557500,"text":"When we thought Masiosare"},{"time":559000,"text":"was the strange enemy,"},{"time":562000,"text":"and we sang, with a childlike heart,"},{"time":564500,"text":"\"a soldier in each son.\""},{"time":569700,"text":"I think the biggest insult,"},{"time":572000,"text":"the worst way you can offend a Mexican"},{"time":574000,"text":"is to insult their mother."},{"time":575800,"text":"A mother is the most sacred thing in life."},{"time":580000,"text":"Mexico is our mother and today she cries out for her children."},{"time":583000,"text":"We are going through the darkest moment"},{"time":586000,"text":"in our recent history."},{"time":588000,"text":"Our mother, Mexico, is being violated before our very eyes."},{"time":591700,"text":"What are we going to do?"},{"time":594700,"text":"Masiosare, the strange enemy, is here."},{"time":597200,"text":"Where is the soldier in each son?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":602000,"text":"Mahatma Gandhi,"},{"time":604000,"text":"one of the greatest civil fighters of all time, said,"},{"time":607800,"text":"\"Be the change you wish to see in the world.\""},{"time":611800,"text":"Today in Mexico we're asking for Gandhis."},{"time":615000,"text":"We need Gandhis."},{"time":617500,"text":"We need men and women who love Mexico"},{"time":620500,"text":"and who are willing to take action."},{"time":623500,"text":"This is a call for every true Mexican"},{"time":628500,"text":"to join this initiative."},{"time":630500,"text":"This is a call"},{"time":632000,"text":"so that every single thing we love about Mexico --"},{"time":635000,"text":"the festivals, the markets,"},{"time":637000,"text":"the restaurants, the cantinas,"},{"time":639000,"text":"the tequila, the mariachis, the serenades,"},{"time":642000,"text":"the posadas, El Grito, the Day of the Dead,"},{"time":645800,"text":"San Miguel, the joy, the passion for life,"},{"time":649200,"text":"the fight and everything it means to be Mexican --"},{"time":653400,"text":"doesn't disappear from this world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657800,"text":"We're facing a very powerful opponent."},{"time":661000,"text":"But we are many more."},{"time":663500,"text":"They can take a man's life."},{"time":666000,"text":"Anyone can kill me,"},{"time":668000,"text":"or you, or you."},{"time":669500,"text":"But no one can kill"},{"time":672000,"text":"the spirit of true Mexicans."},{"time":674500,"text":"The battle is won,"},{"time":676500,"text":"but we still have to fight it."},{"time":679400,"text":"2000 years ago, the Roman poet Juvenal"},{"time":685000,"text":"said something that today echoes"},{"time":688000,"text":"in the heart of every true Mexican."},{"time":691000,"text":"He said, \"Count it the greatest sin"},{"time":695300,"text":"to prefer life to honor,"},{"time":701000,"text":"and for the sake of living"},{"time":705000,"text":"to lose what makes life worth living.\""},{"time":708600,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":710000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}